Arrays:
Arrays are collections of multiple variables.
These variable have index which help us retrieve and store data inside the array.
Why should we use Arrays;
When we have a lot data storing it inside varibles is not feasible.

Syntax:
Approach 1

Datatype [] ArrayName= =new DataType[Size];
int [] numbers=new int[5];

Approach 2 //когда нам извесно и не приизодет изминение
int [] ArrayName={element1,element2,element3,element4}
// int [] number={10,20,30,40,50}